{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":null,"text":"好轻功，果然不愧是飞狐！","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你还能不能站起来？","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你真是来救我的？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":9,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你先跟我走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"还有丁灵琳。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你还要带她走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"刚才还有人说，我这人最大的毛病，就是心太软。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"现在你的腿也很软。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"幸好小丁只不过是被点了穴道，你只要拍开她的穴道就行了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"只不过你出手千万不能像杨天那么重，我并不想要个死老婆。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":null,"text":"这地方好冷。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"冷比不冷好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"因为你总算还活着，死人就不会觉得冷了。","tone":"淡然","chapter":9,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"不管怎么样，能活着总是不坏的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":9,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"实在不坏。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你的鼻子怎么样了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"还在疼。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"我的鼻子若还在痛时，我就绝不会去救那个打扁我鼻子的人。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":9,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"也许我的心比你还软。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"幸好你的心并不坏。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你知不知道一件事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":98,"line_end":98}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yang_tian","name":"杨天","alias":["飞狐"],"identity":"冷香园中好手，外号飞狐","faction":"faction_wei_tian_peng","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"外号飞狐的银光练子枪手，被韩贞一招点穴击败。","personality":{"traits":["轻功出众","枪法凌厉","骄傲","急躁","自负","遇强则乱"],"speech_style":"寡言","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_han_zhen","type":"对手","intensity":70,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"被一招制服"},{"target":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"从属"}],"known_skills":["skill_lian_zi_qiang"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":6,"line_end":36,"text":"杨天没有回头，身子陡然拔起，凌空翻身，贴在屋顶上。"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_lian_zi_qiang","name":"练子枪","type":"暗器","faction":"faction_wei_tian_peng","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"软兵刃练子枪，可抖直可缠绕，杨天在此道上已下二十年苦功。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_lian_zi_qiang_ci_hou","name":"直刺咽喉","type":"attack","description":"将软兵刃练子枪反手抖得笔直，直刺对手咽喉。"},{"id":"tech_lian_zi_qiang_hua_tai","name":"滑台贴壁","type":"feint","description":"在屋顶滑出一丈，贴墙壁滑下，绕到敌人背后。"}],"progression":[],"effects":[],"combat_style":"软兵刃近身缠斗，攻守兼备。","rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":16,"line_end":26,"text":"反腕从腰畔拿下了条银光闪闪的练子枪……至少已有二十年的功夫。"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_di_shi_leng_xiang_yuan","name":"冷香园地室","region":"冷香园","one_line":"冷香园内一处地下石室，阴暗潮湿，仅有一扇门通往上面。","source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":68,"line_end":72,"text":"地室里阴暗潮湿，而且冷得要命。幸好屋角还有张木板床。"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"我见过很多当地的武林高手，都可以算是一等一的高手，那其中武功最高的一个你知不知道是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是我！","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你好像并不太谦虚。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我一向很坦白。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"所以我奇怪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":112,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"奇怪我太坦白？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"奇怪的事很多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你可以一件件的说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"听说你中了一动就死的毒，现在你动了，却还活着。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":122,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"无论什么毒，都有解药。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"连魔教的毒你也能解？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我还活着。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"所以我在奇怪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"奇怪我还能活着？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"奇怪你活得并不好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我活得为什么不好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"像你这样的人，本该活得更好些的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":140,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你是说，我本不该在卫天鹏门下讨饭吃的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"卫天鹏并不是个很好的主人，你本不该如此委屈自己，更不该站在那里挨我一拳的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":146,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我有原因。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"我知道其中一定有原因。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我在避仇。","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"避仇？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我的仇家绝对想不到我会避在卫天鹏家里做食客。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你本来的名字不是韩贞？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你的仇家是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":170,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是个很可怕的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"我想得到，连你这种人都在躲避他，他当然可怕。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"那么你也该想到，我为什么要救你了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"你想要我助你一臂之力，对付你的仇家？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我知道你是个很有用的朋友，也是个恩怨分明的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"我也不想太谦虚。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":182,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"一个恩怨分明的人，为了报那救命之恩，往往什么事都肯做的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":184,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"那么你现在至少应该告诉我，你究竟要我做什么。","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":188,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"以后我当然会告诉你，现在……","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":190,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你受的伤好像并不重，怎么连站都站不起来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"因为我还没有喝酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":196,"line_end":196},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"现在你想喝？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":198,"line_end":198},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"喝了酒之后，我的心也许会更软，腿却绝不会软了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":200,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_han_zhen","updates":{"one_line":"假名韩贞，本名不详；为避仇家冒充卫天鹏门下食客，真实武功极高，连魔教之毒亦能解。"},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_ye_kai","type":"合作者","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"以救命之恩要挟叶开助拳"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":296,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"酒能治你的伤？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":204,"line_end":204},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"我受的伤很特别。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":206,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我相信有很多人，一定都愿意受你这种伤的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"好，我去替你找酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_han_zhen","text":"酒不能少。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"下酒菜也不能少，最好再找套男人衣服来，我实在看不惯他这种不男不女的样子。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_han_zhen","speaker_name":"韩贞","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"你的样子好像也跟他差不多。","tone":"淡然","chapter":9,"line_start":220,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"除了我们两个人外，只有上官小仙知道我们的行动，我们本该想到消息是她故意泄漏出去的，这本是件很明显的事。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"也许就因为太明显了，所以我们才想不到。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":9,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我们也应该想到，上官金虹和林仙儿的女儿若是白痴，天下的人都应该是白痴了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"她一定已把我们看成白痴。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":9,"line_start":240,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"看来她好像比她的爹娘还厉害。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"上官金虹太专横，林仙儿太软弱，这两种毛病她却没有。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":244,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"但她还是有弱点的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她若没有弱点，我们怎么能到这里来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"她惟一做错了的事，就是她低估了韩贞。","tone":"认真","chapter":9,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我不喜欢这个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":256,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"不喜欢韩贞？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"嗯！","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":260,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"他也并不要你喜欢他。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":262,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这也许只因为他知道我快要做你老婆了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":264,"line_end":264},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"你说什么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":9,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你说你不想要个死老婆，我现在并没有死。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":270,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"你这个人的耳朵倒真长。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":272,"line_end":272},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我虽然不能动，也不能说话，但你们说的话，我每句都听得清清楚楚。","tone":"得意","chapter":9,"line_start":274,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"哦！","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":278,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"那个人要喂你吃奶的时候，我真恨不得咬她一口。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":9,"line_start":280,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"老实说，我也很想咬她一口。","tone":"无奈","chapter":9,"line_start":284,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"老实说，你准备在什么时候娶我？","tone":"娇声","chapter":9,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"在你不吃醋的时候。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":290,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"傻瓜，女人若不吃醋，就不是女人了，这道理你都不懂。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":292,"line_end":292}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":297,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":null,"text":"他不懂，他只会杀人。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":null,"text":"一夜中就杀了八十三个人，好大的手笔，好大的气魄。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"你以为人都是我杀的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我只知道他们都死了，你却还活着。","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"活着的并不止我一个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只有你一个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"你没有看见别的人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":348,"line_end":348},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"上官小仙呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":350,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"我正想问你们，她在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"我们怎么会知道她在哪里？我们也在躲着她。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":null,"text":"她本是跟着你们来的，你们却在躲着她？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"不错，她是跟我们来的，那只不过因为我们也上了她的当。","tone":"激动","chapter":9,"line_start":364,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"人都是她杀的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"她为什么不连你们也一起杀了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":372,"line_end":372},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"因为韩贞将我们救了出来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"韩贞呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"找酒去了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"这种时候，你们还想喝酒，他还肯去替你找酒？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"你不信？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"上官小仙杀人的时候，你们都在旁边看着？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"因为我也被她点了穴道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"他也中了暗算，全身已连一点力气都没有，怎么能……","tone":"激动","chapter":9,"line_start":390,"line_end":390},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你已连一点力气都没有？","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":394,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你若真的已连一点力气都没有，我就杀了你。","tone":"厉声","chapter":9,"line_start":402,"line_end":402}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yi_ye_ku","name":"伊夜哭","alias":["赤魔"],"identity":"江湖怪客，面如僵尸，穿着绣黑牡丹的鲜红长袍","faction":null,"role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"面如僵尸的红袍怪客，赤魔手主人，与青魔日哭齐名，自承杀人八十三。","personality":{"traits":["阴鸷","凶残","孤僻","自负","口齿伶俐","煽动力强","目中无人"],"speech_style":"阴阳怪气，语速不快而寒意逼人","temperament":"阴冷酷烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ye_kai","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"扬言要杀叶开"},{"target":"char_ri_ku","type":"宿敌","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"青魔日哭赤魔夜哭齐名"},{"target":"char_guo_ding","type":"对手","intensity":80,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"诱劝联手未果"}],"known_skills":["skill_chi_mo_shou"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":310,"line_end":336,"text":"这个人看来就像是个僵尸……一夜中就杀了八十三个人。"}]},{"id":"char_ri_ku","name":"日哭","alias":["青魔"],"identity":"与赤魔夜哭齐名的青魔","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"assassin","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"青魔日哭，与伊夜哭齐名，并称'青魔日哭，赤魔夜哭'。","personality":{"traits":["神秘","与赤魔齐名","未登场"],"speech_style":"未登场","temperament":"未登场"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yi_ye_ku","type":"宿敌","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"青魔赤魔齐名"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":452,"line_end":454,"text":"青魔日哭，赤魔夜哭，天地皆哭，日月不出！"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_chi_mo_shou","name":"赤魔手","type":"掌法","faction":null,"rank":"出神入化","one_line":"赤魔伊夜哭的血红色手掌，中者必死，袖底出招可挥人撞墙。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_chi_mo_shou_xiu_di_chu_zhao","name":"袖底出招","type":"attack","description":"长袖一挥，将对手挥出撞墙。"},{"id":"tech_chi_mo_shou_xue_hong_zhua","name":"血红一抓","type":"attack","description":"血红的手闪电般抓向咽喉，中者必死。"}],"progression":[],"effects":[{"type":"伤害","description":"中者必死无疑"}],"combat_style":"以诡异长袖配合血红魔手突袭，近身一击必杀。","rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":410,"line_end":418,"text":"这人的手已从长袖中伸出……红魔手！无论谁只要被红魔手一抓，都必死无疑。"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":500,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"我也不懂。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":9,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":null,"text":"你是不是只懂得杀人？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":434,"line_end":434},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"青魔日哭，赤魔夜哭，天地皆哭，日月不出！","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"我知道你。","tone":"淡然","chapter":9,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"我也知道你。","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"哦！","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你是嵩阳郭家的人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"郭定。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"嵩阳铁剑，杀人无算，只怕还比不上这个人。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":468,"line_end":468},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"叶开？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"想不到你也知道他。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"一夜之间，连伤八十三条人命，这并不容易。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"但他一口否认。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"据他说杀人的凶手是上官小仙。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":480,"line_end":480},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"上官小仙是个白痴，世上没有杀人的白痴。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":482,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你不信？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":484,"line_end":484},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"不信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"他说他自己也险些死在上官小仙手里，只怕他已全无丝毫力气。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"他看来并不像中了暗算的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":492,"line_end":492},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你不信？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":494,"line_end":494},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"不信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"他说他现在还活着，只不过因为韩贞救了他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":498,"line_end":498}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_guo_ding","name":"郭定","alias":["嵩阳铁剑"],"identity":"嵩阳郭家之人，嵩阳铁剑郭嵩阳之后，身背黑色长剑","faction":"faction_song_yang_guo_jia","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"嵩阳铁剑郭嵩阳之后，身背黑剑的黑衣人，与伊夜哭在地室对峙。","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","冷静","慎言","坚毅","嫉恶如仇","不轻信"],"speech_style":"短促冷峻，言简意赅","temperament":"刚直内敛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_yi_ye_ku","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"怒斥其侮辱郭嵩阳"},{"target":"char_guo_song_yang","type":"亲属","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"嵩阳铁剑郭嵩阳之后"},{"target":"char_ye_kai","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"暂未动手，等韩贞"},{"target":"char_yang_tian","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"杨天为其友"}],"known_skills":["skill_song_yang_tie_jian"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":436,"line_end":466,"text":"是个高大魁伟的黑衣人，身后背着柄长剑……郭定。"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_song_yang_tie_jian","name":"嵩阳铁剑","type":"剑法","faction":"faction_song_yang_guo_jia","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"兵器谱排名第四，郭嵩阳的成名剑法，郭定虽未及先祖亦颇可观。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_song_yang_tie_jian_lv_di","name":"嵩阳剑意","type":"attack","description":"嵩阳铁剑的剑意传承自郭嵩阳。"},{"id":"tech_song_yang_tie_jian_jing_rang","name":"惊艳一握","type":"special","description":"翻手腕握住剑柄，出剑前的标志性动作。"}],"progression":[],"effects":[{"type":"伤害","description":"嵩阳铁剑杀人无算"}],"combat_style":"嵩阳郭家世代传承的铁剑剑法。","rag_refs":[9],"source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":466,"line_end":474,"text":"郭定……嵩阳铁剑，杀人无算，只怕还比不上这个人。"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_song_yang_guo_jia","name":"嵩阳郭家","type":"家族","location":"嵩阳","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"嵩阳郭家，世代传承嵩阳铁剑，曾于兵器谱排名第四。","source_refs":[{"chapter":9,"line_start":464,"line_end":470,"text":"你是嵩阳郭家的人？……嵩阳铁剑，杀人无算。"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":501,"line_end":638,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"据我所知，韩贞才是中了暗算的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":500,"line_end":500},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"他说韩贞此刻不在这里，是替他找酒去了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"现在好像并不是喝酒的时候。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":504,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"他说的话你完全不信？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":506,"line_end":506},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"完全不信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"我也不信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":510,"line_end":510},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你们知道韩贞受了暗算，知道上官小仙是跟我们来的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"这些事是谁告诉你们的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":520,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"一个侥幸未死的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":522,"line_end":522},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"杨天？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":524,"line_end":524},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你怎么知道他说的是真话？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"他是我的朋友。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":530,"line_end":530},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你有这么样的朋友，真是走运了。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":532,"line_end":532},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"他虽然不是我的朋友，他的话我也相信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":534,"line_end":534},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":536,"line_end":536},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"事实俱在，我不能不信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":538,"line_end":538},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"什么事实？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"你们杀了所有知道内情的人，藏起了上官小仙，准备以后再嫁祸给别人，金钱帮的宝藏岂非就已稳稳的落入你们手里？","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"你说的话若有人证明，我也相信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":550,"line_end":550},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"我们说的话，幸好还有一个人可以证明。","tone":"微笑","chapter":9,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"韩贞？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":556,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":558,"line_end":558},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"他去替你们找酒去了？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":560,"line_end":560},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"不错。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_ling_lin","text":"既然只不过是去找酒，当然很快就会回来。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":564,"line_end":564},{"speaker":"char_ding_ling_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你最好等他回来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":566,"line_end":566},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"好，我们等。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":568,"line_end":568},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你真的要等？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":570,"line_end":570},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"我已说过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"等他们的帮手来，将我们也一起杀了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"你是你，我是我，并不是我们。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":576,"line_end":576},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你莫非还不曾与我为伍？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":578,"line_end":578},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"昔年嵩阳铁剑在兵器谱中排名第四，的确可以算是了不起的大英雄，只可惜……","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":584,"line_end":584},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"只可惜怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":586,"line_end":586},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"只可惜你并不是郭嵩阳，郭嵩阳的尸首只怕早已化成灰了。","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":588,"line_end":588},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"死人就是死人，所有的死人都一样，莫忘记大剑客死了，尸身也跟别人一样会腐烂发臭的。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":594,"line_end":594},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"你最好也莫要忘记一件事。","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":598,"line_end":598},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"什么事。","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":600,"line_end":600},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"郭嵩阳虽死了，嵩阳铁剑却没有死。","tone":"厉声","chapter":9,"line_start":602,"line_end":602},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"嵩阳铁剑难道还想带着这杀人的凶手来对付我？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":604,"line_end":604},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"郭嵩阳是死在荆无命剑下的，荆无命的剑法，传自上官金虹。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":608,"line_end":608},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你若是郭家的好子孙，就该与我联手，除了叶开，找出上官小仙，再从上官金虹手上的武功秘笈中，找出他们剑法中的瑕疵，与荆无命决一胜负，为郭嵩阳死后的英灵出一口气。","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":614,"line_end":614},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你的意思如何？","tone":"沉声","chapter":9,"line_start":622,"line_end":622},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"很好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":624,"line_end":624},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你已答应？","tone":"疑问","chapter":9,"line_start":626,"line_end":626},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_yi_ye_ku","text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":9,"line_start":628,"line_end":628},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"只要你我联手，别说区区一个叶开，放眼天下，又有谁能与我们较一日之短长？","tone":"大笑","chapter":9,"line_start":630,"line_end":630},{"speaker":"char_yi_ye_ku","speaker_name":"伊夜哭","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这地方别无退路，看来今日你已死定了。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":9,"line_start":636,"line_end":636}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_guo_song_yang","name":"郭嵩阳","alias":["嵩阳铁剑"],"identity":"嵩阳郭家先祖，兵器谱中排名第四，死于荆无命剑下","faction":"faction_song_yang_guo_jia","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"嵩阳铁剑郭嵩阳，兵器谱排名第四的传奇剑客，已死于荆无命剑下。","personality":{"traits":["豪迈","大英雄","剑术绝顶","已故","被后人敬仰"],"speech_style":"未登场